# API HTTP test requests for VS code REST client

### Get all cats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/cats

### Get cat by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/cats/41
Content-Type: application/json

### Get static file
GET http://localhost:3000/public/index.html


### Create new cat
POST  http://localhost:3000/api/v1/cats
Content-Type: application/json

  {
    "cat_name": "Kittens",
    "weight": 8,
    "birthdate": "2021-10-12",
    "filename": "https://loremflickr.com/320/240/cat3",
     "owner": 3602
  }

### Update cat Info
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/cats/9590
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "cat_name": "cute Kittens",
    "weight": 8,
    "birthdate": "2021-10-12",
    "filename": "https://loremflickr.com/320/240/cat3",
     "owner": 3602
  }

### Delete cat
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/cats/9594



// Users

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users

### Get user by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/3609
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new user
POST  http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

  {

    "name": "Alice Smith",
    "username": "alicesmith",
    "email": "alice@metropolia.fi",
    "role": "user",
    "password": "password"
  }

